00:07:15.768 --> 00:07:17.854
- Remember to finish it!
- Pan Xin Tong!

00:07:17.854 --> 00:07:19.522
Pan Xin Tong!

00:07:19.522 --> 00:07:21.315
I...

00:07:21.315 --> 00:07:22.824
Hey, I...

