of emotional agitation.

00:18:28.065 --> 00:18:30.984
Dr. Liao said she'll be fine after some rest.

00:18:30.984 --> 00:18:34.321
But if your mom leaves
without permission again,

00:18:34.321 --> 00:18:35.989
we'll ask you to transfer to another hospital.

00:18:35.989 --> 00:18:37.783
I'm sorry. I apologize.

00:18:37.783 --> 00:18:39.993
I'm really sorry for the trouble.

00:18:39.993 --> 00:18:41.920
I'll leave her to you.

00:18:46.792 --> 00:18:49.670
