and apologizing for you since I was little.

00:19:49.771 --> 00:19:51.273
You're my mom.

00:19:51.273 --> 00:19:53.692
Shouldn't you be taking care of me?

00:19:53.692 --> 00:19:56.320
All you do is cause trouble every day.

00:19:56.320 --> 00:19:59.497
If possible, I really don't want
to be your daughter.

00:20:40.892 --> 00:20:44.973
[Living Will for Palliative Care
and Life-Sustaining Treatment]

00:20:44.973 --> 00:20:46.602
