just wrap me up and throw me in the garbage.

00:21:10.102 --> 00:21:12.569
That's not what I meant.

00:21:16.358 --> 00:21:19.528
I know I'm not a good mom.

00:21:20.153 --> 00:21:22.614
I can't protect you either.

00:21:22.614 --> 00:21:26.201
The most I can do is beat people up for you.

00:21:26.201 --> 00:21:29.003
I just hope that sometimes,

00:21:29.579 --> 00:21:34.036
my daughter can talk to me.

00:21:36.169 --> 00:21:39.089
She can talk to me about her life.

00:21:39.089 --> 00:21:42.637
When she's sad, I can comfort her.

00:21:48.765 --> 00:21:50.473
