- Go on.
- Are you thirsty?

00:42:32.258 --> 00:42:35.177
No.

00:42:35.177 --> 00:42:36.720
Go on, get back to work.

00:42:36.720 --> 00:42:39.647
Are you feeling unwell?
Tell me if you are.

