It's not as bad as when I gave birth to you.

00:42:45.020 --> 00:42:49.250
You're the culprit who caused me so much pain.

00:42:50.484 --> 00:42:52.361
I've never given birth. How would I know?

00:42:52.361 --> 00:42:56.240
After I give birth,
I'll tell you if it hurts, okay?

00:42:56.240 --> 00:42:57.533
Then hurry up and give birth.

00:42:57.533 --> 00:42:59.785
Don't make me wait too long.

00:42:59.785 --> 00:43:01.412
Get well soon.

00:43:01.412 --> 00:43:03.163
You'll have to take care of the kids later.

